highlights

Timeline

Program Manager at Amazon Web Services 2021/07-2021/09

Led a team of 7 developers to engineer and deploy Boost (AWS Product) in APAC, achieved final milestone a week prior to expected time. Examined thousands of customers feed-back to propose a change in market strategy, resulted in a 8% client conversion rate increase. Facilitated cross-functional collaborations between Marketing, Engineering, and Sales teams to design and build the AWS China's official webpage.

Analyst at SOSV 2021/02-2021/06

I am working as an associate intern under SOSV's investment associate and Global Partnership Manager. I formulate localization strategies for foreign start-ups to enter the Chinese market. So far, my proposed strategies have been adopted by 6 out of 7 companies. I also source and screen potential deals of size $150k to $1.5million for SOSV's China Accelerator and MOX.

Algorithm Engineer at JD.com 202/10-2021/02

Researched consumer trends and analyzed current strategies, and engineered a sales strategy recommender model trusted by 30+ major malls across the country. Developed document detection and NLP models to automate text classification on JD's shopping mall platform, saving 1,100,000 yuan/year in labor cost.

Data Science & Automation Intern at Safran 2020/06-2020/09

- Safran is a Fortune 500 Company focused on Defense, Aerospace, and Security. Engineered software to automate aircraft & rocket engines production flow and manufacturing robots’ data collection, decreased overall throughput time by 10%. Created sustainable PowerBI and Highcharts applications that enabled finance, engineering and purchase departments to make data-driven decisions.

Data Science Intern at ForkaiA 2020/05-2020/07

ForkaiA is a startup accelerator based in UCI Research Park, California. I was a data scientist who consulted for its startups. I identified possible applications of ML for its new startups, as well as trained and optimize existing models. The internship turned remote midway due to Covid 19.

CTO at Canine Voice 2018/09-2019/05

Canine Voice is a company providing customized alarm system for service dog handlers. As its cofounder and CTO, I led all development efforts and created products that sustained $3,800+ in monthly sales over 6 months. I also took the initiative of creating an engaging website(React, Node,Mongo) coupled with social media campaigns(instagram facebook) which generated a total of 100,000 views.
